document.full_text: tunisia's election will be delayed until october 23, a week later than the date suggested by electoral officials, to ensure it can be "free and transparent," prime minister beji caid sebsi said on wednesday.
document.title: tunisia election delayed until october 23
lines_and_colors: tunisia's election will be delayed until october 23, a week later than the date suggested by electoral officials, to ensure it can be "free and transparent," prime minister beji caid sebsi said on wednesday.
